$$ title

.LOD File Format

$$ body

This page will deal with .lod file format that can be found in Heroes of Might and Magic 3

## LOD Header

* +0x00 : Magic 	(DWORD) 	// "LOD" : 0x00444f4c
* +0x04 : Type		(DWORD)
* +0x08 : NbFile	(DWORD)
* +0x0C : Unknown	(BYTE [80])
* +0x5C : h3file	(struct h3file[10000])

## H3 File Struct

* +0x00 : Name 		(BYTE [16])
* +0x10 : Offset	(DWORD)
* +0x14 : RealSize	(DWORD)
* +0x18 : Type		(DWORD)
* +0x1C : CompSize	(DWORD)

